parameters: Just browse through it before it's time

Welcome to the Anime Club of Yume Sakura high school!
欢迎来到梦樱高校漫研部！
Do you wanna play our original games?
要玩玩我们的原创游戏吗！
Yes, but not now, I don't have enough time
虽然挺感兴趣的，不过时间好像不太够
No worries, you can come to Anime Club to try it in any time
没关系的，之后随时都可以来漫研部体验！
BTW, recently I want some recommendation of good manga
对了，最近有什么好看的漫画推荐吗
You are asking a right person
We're all really into creepy manga these days
我们最近都非常喜欢惊悚漫画
Is it about blood, horror, ghosts or something?
就是那种血腥的恐怖漫画吗？
Included, but sometimes blood and horror are not necessary for a creepy manga
当然也包括这一类，不过对于惊悚漫画来说，血腥和恐怖都不是必须的呢
However, I prefer a manga that are full of conflicts and mysteries
不过我还是更喜欢充满矛盾和未知的题材
You must come to Anime Club in the future, I'll give you a lot of recommendations!
到时候来漫研部，我给你推荐几本！
You don't want to miss it!
Freelyn hasn't told me where she went

或许是像昨天那样自己呆在帐篷里吧
